Package ntnu.idatt2001.ejhaslerjorgfi.ui.views

Class EngineScene

java.lang.Object
ntnu.idatt2001.ejhaslerjorgfi.ui.views.EngineScene
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameScene, GoalsInfoScene, HomeScene, PlayerInfoScene, StoryInfoScene, TutorialScene
public abstract class EngineScene extends Object

EngineScene

An abstract class which defines the required fields and methods for all Scene-classes in this application. It acts as a superclass which classes such as PlayerInfoScene is a subclass of. The classes which inherits from this class will override the methods of this class and specify the contents in the given fields.
